1.title: Fashion Roots
1.plot: Style Factory gets the skinny on the Roots varsity jacket, La Canadienne's suede ankle boot, Eric Javits' high-tech fedora, and Hanky Panky's revolutionary thong.

2.title: Turning Heads
2.plot: Style Factory has the inside scoop on New Balance 998 sneakers, Vela high-fashion headscarves, the President's Frank Clegg briefcase, and Canadian dressmaker Lucian Matis.

3.title: American Icons
3.plot: Style Factory unveils the incredible story behind the Schott NYC Perfecto motorcycle jacket, Zkano knee-high socks, the Stetson cowboy hat, and Mark Anthony Strictly Curls Curl Envy cream.

4.title: Atomic Proportions
4.plot: Style Factory pulls back the curtain on Shan's shapely bikini, L.L. Bean's iconic duck boots, the Christy Dawn midi dress, and Dean Davidson's bold bangles.

5.title: Rocker Chic
5.plot: Style Factory gets the skinny on Dennis Basso's beaded gowns, Mo's Bows' feel-good bowties, the rock'n'roll Jet Boot from Modern Vice, and dazzling purple eyeshadow from Caryl Baker Visage.

6.title: Under Armor
6.plot: Style Factory gets the goods on Randolph's Air Force-tested aviators, the slinky Celeste slip from Farr West, a rockin' leather backpack from M0851, and the Mayan Cross necklace from Sweet Romance Jewelry.

7.title: Head to Toes
7.plot: Style Factory walks the catwalk in New Era baseball caps, a sexy Nicole Miller cocktail dress, Miik's classic black leggings, and Haute Red nail polish from Orly.

8.title: Reinvented Classics
8.plot: Style Factory has the inside scoop on the Weird Guy jean, a sexy crop top from MDS Stripes, Red Alert lipstick from Quo Cosmetics, and the architecturally-inspired crib coat by Yeohlee.

9.title: Tailored Fit
9.plot: Style Factory has the skinny on the world-famous Cendrillon ballet flat, Lipson's crisp white shirt, Grande Naturals' caffeinated lip plumper, and a lacy black bra named Lucy.

10.title: Blushing Bride
10.plot: Style Factory gets the goods on a long-lasting blush from Too Faced Cosmetics, Amsale Aberra's couture wedding gowns, Birdwell Beach Britches' classic board shorts, and Gigi New York's Kelly saddlebag.

11.title: Dress to Impress
11.plot: Style Factory reveals the story behind L.A. Made's subtle tie-dyed tee, Austin Scarlett's strapless cocktail dress, Parfumerie Galimard's latest fragrance, and Oak Street Bootmakers natural trench boot.

12.title: Power Dressing
12.plot: Style Factory has the inside scoop on the celebrity-inspired Yoko pant, K. Jacques' legendary gladiator sandal, Piccadilly Fashions' pencil skirt, and the Pietro bucket bag.

13.title: Head Over Heels
13.plot: Style Factory has the goods on Rupert Sanderson's Elba stilettos, Laparka's high fashion parka, the little black Edie dress from Project Gravitas, and Duchess of Fabulous chandelier earrings.

14.title: Timeless Classics
14.plot: Style Factory gets the scoop on Twenty Tees' romper suit, Laulhère's iconic French beret, the wash-and-wear blazer from Tristan, and the luxurious Tag Heuer Calibre 01 wristwatch.

imdb.plot outline: Style Factory offers an addictive behind-the-scenes look at how fashion and beauty products are made. With fashionistas and company insiders weighing in at every step, the series reveals the incredible stories behind the items we need and covet most. From the accessible to the aspirational, it's a rare chance to peer behind the curtains of our favourite brands where crafty artisans work their magic and mass production dazzles.
